rows.label: qst102211_msg0001
rows.name: So you're the one Nis was talking to.

rows.label: qst102211_msg0002
rows.name:
You fought alongside
Vandham, right? I've heard.

rows.label: qst102211_msg0003
rows.name:
I'm Kathira. I'm one of
the veterans around here.

rows.label: qst102211_msg0020
rows.name: Nis is so young, yet he's so cautious.

rows.label: qst102211_msg0021
rows.name:
Squad Chief Corden always tells
me I'm too reckless, so maybe
we'll make a good pair.

rows.label: qst102211_msg0102
rows.name:
I think I've gathered some in
the area with the spores, in
the middle of the cavern.

rows.label: qst102211_msg0301
rows.name:
Give the ingredients to Nis,
okay? Ah, I'm starving~!

rows.label: qst102211_msg0201
rows.name: Phew, I'm stuffed! That was delicious!

rows.label: qst102211_msg0202
rows.name:
The next mission is going
to be tough, but I feel
like I can handle it now.
